node.text: We just delivered the final commercial #G550. During its nearly two decades in service, the G550 set a new standard for performance and reliability and continues to outperform and impress with its wide-ranging capabilities. #ArtOfExcellence

node.text: To new heights — each look at the sky is a reminder of opportunity. #FanFriday by @alangrubelic.
